From your browser, understand the status of yourBI and analytics dashboards based on the context from your data.world  cataloged resources. This will appear as a “Hoot,” or trust badge, on your dashboard or resource if it’s cataloged in data.world. Quickly connect to your data.world instance to see status notifications, glossary terms, and more. Easily jump from the Hoot to the catalog to view lineage and resource details.

Your use of this browser extension is governed by the terms and conditions of your enterprise agreement with data.world, Inc. for its Services and the Privacy Policy found at Privacy, as such agreements and policies are amended from time to time. You need a data.world account to use the data.world browser plugin.
